Package: libretro-craft
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Depends: retroarch | libretro-frontend, ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: Libretro wrapper for Craft
 This wrapper makes Craft compatible with libretro, thus allowing its use
 with libretro frontends, such as RetroArch.
 .
 Craft is a Minecraft clone for Windows, Mac OS X and Linux. It is written
 in just a few thousand lines of C and uses modern OpenGL (shaders). Online
 multiplayer support is included using a Python-based server. 
